		    <img src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/7/21/1405925714746/084b2599-9e43-4872-b846-43c91f39986c-460x371.jpeg" alt="Pythagoras Twitter" width="460" height="371" class="gu-image" />
		                    <figcaption>
                    <span class="element-image__caption">Pythagoras on Twitter.</span>
                                    </figcaption>
